 have the 150 gal in my bedroom. Let me tell you it does wonders for you when you would like to relax.<br>
<br>
  I also have 3 terruariums set up in my home also. One is filled with a Rosy haired tarantula. Tarantulas are awsome pets and great to look at aswell. My coffee table is made into a terruarium also. It contians 4 lepord gecko's. I had a blast making this. They are also great to have.<br>
<br>
  My third one is my Red haired baboon tarantula also in my main living room. That is in a hexed terruarium and stands 3 ' tall.<br>
<br>
   My 55 gal salt water tank is filled with  non aggresive fish . This tank is also reef tank. Have lots of sea enimes and starfish  much much more.<br>
<br>
  The 150 gal tank is an aggressive tank and boy oh boy the are fun tanks to have. You will get  alot of enjoyment out of an aggressive tank.<br>
<br>
  Either way you go   just remember it can be a bit expensive and does take some time to keep them clean. But the rewards are well worth it.<br>
<br>
